@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ilbamx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.35) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.56)) * ((v1 + 0.76 - tmp + 0.43) / (tmp + 0.64 - v0 + 0.38)))
    tmp = (0.75 + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.97) * v1))
    v0 = 0.73
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.15)) - ((v1 + 0.92 + v1 + 0.61) - (v0 + 0.88 - tmp + 0.43)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.02 + tmp + 0.14)) + 0.30)
    v0 = (0.93 + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.39) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.12)))
    v2 = (v0 / wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = wp.abs((v2 + v0))
    data[tid] = v0
